        "$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000011": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000011",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e02a6fe3d711fc52-8f4a13 twpub-e02a6fe3d711fc52-34f4a1 twpub-e02a6fe3d711fc52-6b4cd0\"><blockquote><div><p><br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000015\">CHAPTER I.</$link>    Reddy Fox Brings Granny News<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000033\">CHAPTER II.</$link>   Granny And Reddy Fox Go Hunting<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000046\">CHAPTER III.</$link>   Reddy Is Sure Granny Has Lost Her Senses<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000067\">CHAPTER IV.</$link>   Quacker The Duck Grows Curious<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000081\">CHAPTER V.</$link>   Reddy Fox Is Afraid To Go Home<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000092\">CHAPTER VI.</$link>   Old Granny Fox Is Caught Napping<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000109\">CHAPTER VII.</$link>   Granny Fox Has A Bad Dream<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000123\">CHAPTER VIII.</$link>   What Farmer Brown's Boy Did<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000137\">CHAPTER IX.</$link>   Reddy Fox Hears About Granny Fox<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000159\">CHAPTER X.</$link>   Reddy Fox Is Impudent<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000176\">CHAPTER XI.</$link>   After The Storm<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000195\">CHAPTER XII.</$link>   Granny And Reddy Fox Hunt In Vain<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000209\">CHAPTER XIII.</$link>   Granny Fox Admits Growing Old<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000227\">CHAPTER XIV.</$link>   Three Vain And Foolish Wishes<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000254\">CHAPTER XVI.</$link>   Reddy Is Made Truly Happy<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000272\">CHAPTER XVII.</$link>   Granny Fox Promises Reddy Bowser's Dinner<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000289\">CHAPTER XVIII.</$link>   Why Bowser The Hound Didn't Eat His Dinner<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000303\">CHAPTER XIX.</$link>   Old Man Coyote Does A Little Thinking<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000316\">CHAPTER XX.</$link>   A Twice Stolen Dinner<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000328\">CHAPTER XXI.</$link>   Granny And Reddy Talk Things Over<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000347\">CHAPTER XXII.</$link>   Granny Fox Plans To Get A Fat Hen<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000368\">CHAPTER XXIII.</$link>   Farmer Brown's Boy Forgets To Close The Gate<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000383\">CHAPTER XXIV.</$link>   A Midnight Visit<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000400\">CHAPTER XXV.</$link>   A Dinner For Two<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000417\">CHAPTER XXVI.</$link>   Farmer Brown's Boy Sets A Trap<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000429\">CHAPTER XXVII.</$link>   Prickly Porky Takes A Sun Bath<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000445\">CHAPTER XXVIII.    </$link>  Prickly Porky Enjoys Himself<br>\n<br>\n<$link class=\"pginternal\" to=\"$:/plugins/twpub/e02a6fe3d711fc52/text/000000467\">CHAPTER XXIX.</$link>   The New Home In The Old Pasture<br>\n<br></p></div></blockquote></div>"
        },
